_sText:
This is my first map so i would apreciate any feedback/suggestions you can offer me.

I wanted to make a map that could be fun when only 2-6 people are on the server, i think i accomplished that. The glass on this map is great, if you see someone using it to get into your spawn you can shoot it from under them and make them fall to their death :)

There are 16 spawn points on this map, but i can not imagine it been any fun for more than 6 players.

I made this map for my clan G4F^ (www.g4fclan.info)

Have fun playing, i know we do!

Known Bugs:
If you make one tower collapse, they both collapse. I have no idea how to fix this.
